Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
HBase - Server Main functionality for HBase
HBase - Thrift HBase Thrift Server
HBase - Shell Shell for HBase
HBase - Protocol Protobuf protocol classes used by HBase to communicate.
HBase - Client Client of HBase
HBase - Hadoop Compatibility Interfaces to be implemented in order to smooth over hadoop version differences
HBase - Common Common functionality for HBase
HBase - Integration Tests Integration and System tests for HBase
HBase - Examples Examples of HBase usage
HBase - Prefix Tree Prefix Tree Data Block Encoder
HBase - Assembly Module that does project assembly and that is all that it does.
HBase - Testing Util HBase Testing Utilities.
HBase - Hadoop Two Compatibility Interfaces to be implemented in order to smooth over hadoop version differences
